G-20 Tells EU Leaders to ‘Decisively’ Address Crisis Oct. 23

-- B y   S i m o n e   M e i e r
-- 
2011-10-15T14:45:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-15/g-20-tells-eu-leaders-to-decisively-address-crisis-oct-23.html
Finance ministers and central bank
governors from the Group of 20 nations said European leaders
should act “decisively” to contain the region’s crisis at a
Brussels summit on Oct. 23, according to a statement handed out
in Paris today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
